                 SSO
              </b>
            </label>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-4"
            data-name="box"
            style="flex-direction: column; display: flex;"
          >
            <div
              data-name="box"
              style="flex-direction: column; display: flex;"
            />
          </div>
          <h4
            class="mt-5 mb-2"
          >
            Auto-join helpdesk
          </h4>
          <p
            class="mb-1"
          >
            Allows people with email addresses in the approved email domains to use the link below to sign up.
          </p>
          <p>
            <a
              href="https://acme.gorgias.com/signup"
            >
              https://acme.gorgias.com/signup
